<title>USA: ESC Medical completes hair removal trials.</title>
<headline>ESC Medical completes hair removal trials.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1996-08-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>ESC Medical Systems Ltd said on Wednesday it had completed clinical trials and filed with the U.S. Food and Drug Administration for permission to commercialize the Epilight Hair Removal system in the United States.</p>
<p>The Epilight System uses ESC's proprietary technology that selectively elliminates hair follicles without damaging the skin, the company said.</p>
